Game type: IDLE RPG style
Components:
  -Lvling :
      * Wave and Level (10 wave with mini boss at the end)
      * Different boss types (Mini,Raid,Epic with boosted drops)
      * Fresh start ( enchant item )
      * No clicking function (everyone hates)
      * Achivment system with lvl up
      * Account lvl
      * Step back in lvls
      
  -Stats:
      * Fighter and Mage stats
      * Accuracy <--> Evasion
      * Elemental stats (fire/water/wind/earth)
      * Hp Regen
  
  -Battle system:
      * Passive and Active Skill
      * Different Classes (heavy, light, robe)
      * Hp regeneration
      * Stats
      * Equipments for classes (heavy, light, robe, weapons)
      
  -Market
  -Hero
  -Equipments
  -Enchant System
  -TopList
  -Craft (misc)
  -Instance (ticket)
  -Donate system
      *AD system
  -Clan/Guild
  -Shop
  -Licit ?
  
  
  Currency: Gold, Ancient Coin, Soul, Gem
  Names: Rebirth
      
